{"tid":2195821,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"奇文分享：仇外本土派有資格說甚麼個體民族主義嗎？他們欠民主運動一個道歉！","createTime":"2020-09-09T11:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T14:57:43.000Z","uid":276028,"like":1,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"524a6a386b95fcfba8709eaf018a63b364a1af5a","tid":2195821,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:50:23.000Z","msg":"原來，自詡是民主捍衛者的盧斯達和中國的憤青及小粉紅一樣，都是狹隘的民族主義者？<br />\n盧斯達曾經攻擊香港歌手何韻詩為何不接受芬蘭人強姦？<br />\n原來只要民主路線和盧斯達不一樣，不願意仇恨中國人，就會被盧斯達攻擊？<br />\n盧斯達的民族主義和中國的憤青及小粉紅竟然無分別？<br />\n現在民主運動四分五裂，盧斯達這些仇外本土派要負責？<br />\n大家若果好奇，就趕緊入來一看！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.boyangu.com/sc/social_science/uglylewisloud02/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boyangu.com%2Fsc%2Fsocial_science%2Fuglylewisloud02%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg4leFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=5470adc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.boyangu.com/sc/social_science/uglylewisloud02/</a>"},{"pid":"fc8c68cbf5de35f8706b5edacf4a9308aa6a210f","tid":2195821,"uid":126889,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:58:49.000Z","msg":"世界應該大愛 開放哂國界 支那畜上網冇牆 任意移民<br />\n共同體冇邊界點得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455e8ca294772da58551f8e03a281c3fe15bdd35","tid":2195821,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:54:10.000Z","msg":"自推。"},{"pid":"2f5e6b99778c90551820e9d7baca698b209d2446","tid":2195821,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:27:53.000Z","msg":"盧斯達之前係熱狗<br />\n攻擊泛民同和理非同其他本土派就梗架啦<br />\n<br />\n依家係咪離開熱狗應該唔係好多人想知"},{"pid":"f879cc0c7eca035214807f6cfb162d0d86f065b0","tid":2195821,"uid":77180,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:42:44.000Z","msg":"又屌盧思達<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好悶呀左狗"},{"pid":"eef4bb5201b0403cbbf338ce0df83f8080fc206d","tid":2195821,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"reply